10 Rem OSS BASIC XL on Atari
20 Rem Note keywords are mixed case.
30 Rem Save text as "HELLO.BXL" and on
40 Rem the Atari Enter the file.
50 Rem Emulators with "H:" device are great for this. 
60 Rem Enter "D:HELLO.BXL" or Enter "H:HELLO.BXL"
70 Rem 
80 Graphics 18 : Rem Mode 2 + 16 for no text window
90 Position 0,0
100 Print #6;"Hello, Whirled!"
110 Goto 110 : Rem Press BREAK to end
